it's a forest of sorts.

00:00:50.573 --> 00:00:56.995
And l know that because
right next to you there's a bear.

00:00:57.288 --> 00:01:02.125
A grizzly, cooling his feet in a stream.

00:01:02.293 --> 00:01:06.630
And all of a sudden,
you begin to deliver...

00:01:06.797 --> 00:01:09.966
...and l can't get to you.

00:01:10.134 --> 00:01:11.927
But the bear can.

00:01:13.679 --> 00:01:15.347
And next thing l know...

00:01:15.515 --> 00:01:20.602
...he is holding our beautiful baby boy.

00:01:20.853 --> 00:01:23.730
And here's where it gets odd. Uh....

00:01:25.441 --> 00:01:27.150
He chews the cord.

00:01:28.402 --> 00:01:30.779
